title: General Electric Falls 3%
text:
General Electric Falls 3%

Stock Markets 14 minutes ago (Oct 01, 2019 11:07AM ET)

© Reuters. General Electric Falls 3% Investing.com - General Electric (NYSE: ) fell by 3.02% to trade at $8.67 by 11:05 (15:05 GMT) on Tuesday on the NYSE exchange. The volume of General Electric shares traded since the start of the session was 15.77M. General Electric has traded in a range of $8.67 to $9.04 on the day. The stock has traded at $9.3900 at its highest and $8.6700 at its lowest during the past seven days.
